<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_CAS_RelativesRelationships" s="315404">
  <T n="name">0x3AAFE84F<!--String: "Relatives & Relationships"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_RelativesAndRelationships_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7436f65542f60d26</T>
      <T n="text">0x6C61411D<!--String: "When creating a new Household, you can decide if the Sims are roomies, relatives, or partners. \n\nBy using the Genetics tool, you can make new Sims that look like your existing Sims by using their “genes”. This is an easy way to add children, parents, and siblings!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_RelativesAndRelationships_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7436f65542f60d25</T>
      <T n="text">0xC54719EB<!--String: "You can set the <b><font color='#199C2C'>relationship</font></b> between your Sims in the Household Relationships menu. \n\nSome relationships are restricted by age; for example, a Sim has to be a Young Adult or older to have children, and their children must be younger than them."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_RelativesAndRelationships_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7436f65542f60d24</T>
      <T n="text">0xA9F576E2<!--String: "You can find the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Play with Genetics</font></b> button in the Add a Sim menu. Selecting this button opens the Genetics panel."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\CAS\CAS_RelativesAndRelationships_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7436f65542f60d23</T>
      <T n="text">0xC2A5BB4C<!--String: "In the Genetics panel, choose a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Relationship</font></b> (Child, Sibling, or Parent), pick <b><font color='#199C2C'>who</font></b> they are related to, select <b><font color='#199C2C'>Gender</font></b> and <b><font color='#199C2C'>Age</font></b>, and roll your new Sim by clicking the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Randomize</font></b> button.\n\n\nIf you like the result, select the Done button to add the new Sim to your Household."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_AddingSimsAndRelationships_3.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:46f250dd7357b8b7</T>
      <T n="text">0x34CD061A<!--String: "When creating a Sim by Playing with Genetics, <b><font color='#199C2C'>relationships</font></b> are automatically applied."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
